                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8024" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1241</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">3275 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">品牌突围：没有“科技与狠活”的汇源果汁涅槃重生</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Brand breakthrough: no &quot;technology and hard work&quot; of Huiyuan juice nirvana rebirth</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张向先，张宇星</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吉林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国汇源果汁集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">汇源；品牌定位；品牌整合营销；品牌资产</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Huiyuan; Brand positioning; Integrated Brand Marketing; Brand assets</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">汇源果汁创建于1992年，自创立起就以“喝汇源果汁，走健康之路”的广告语火遍全国，是国内家喻户晓的国民果汁品牌。但在遭受可口可乐并购失败及港股退市两大重创后，宣告破产，沉寂多年。然而，汇源果汁集团在自身经营不善的情况下，多年来仍然坚持产品中不添加海克斯科技，践行“营养大众，惠及三农”的企业使命。视频博主辛吉飞一句“汇源果汁不含科技与狠活”事件的意外走红，又将汇源重新送回大众视野。汇源果汁集团积极抓住机遇，通过采取事件营销、渠道营销、产品营销等一系列品牌整合营销策略，成功在激烈的果汁饮料市场竞争中突出重围，实现了涅槃重生。本案例描述了汇源果汁集团的发家、破产、后巧借机遇，通过一系列品牌整合营销措施推动企业在激烈的市场竞争中实现品牌突围的全过程。通过对本案例的思考和学习，可以使学生了解品牌定位、品牌整合营销、品牌资产五星模型的相关知识，学习汇源果汁的品牌突围经验，为更好建设本土老字号品牌提供了更多讨论空间和借鉴意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Huiyuan Juice was founded in 1992 and has been popular nationwide since its inception with the slogan &quot;Drink Huiyuan Juice and Walk the Path of Health&quot;. It is a well-known national juice brand in China. But after suffering two major setbacks: the failure of Coca Cola&#39;s acquisition and the delisting of Hong Kong stocks, it declared bankruptcy and remained silent for many years. However, Huiyuan Juice Group still insists on not adding Hex Technology to its products for many years despite its poor operation, and has fulfilled its corporate mission of &quot;nourishing the public and benefiting agriculture, rural areas and farmers&quot;. The unexpected rise to fame of video blogger Xin Jifei&#39;s statement &quot;Huiyuan Juice does not contain technology and ruthlessness&quot; has brought Huiyuan back to the public eye. Huiyuan Juice Group actively seized the opportunity and successfully broke through the fierce competition in the juice beverage market by adopting a series of brand integration marketing strategies such as event marketing, channel marketing, and product marketing, achieving a rebirth. This case describes the entire process of Huiyuan Juice Group&#39;s rise, bankruptcy, and later seizing opportunities to promote brand breakthrough in fierce market competition through a series of brand integration marketing measures. Through thinking and learning about this case, students can understand the relevant knowledge of brand positioning, brand integrated marketing, and the five-star model of brand assets. They can also learn about the brand breakthrough experience of Huiyuan Juice, providing more discussion space and reference significance for better building local time-honored brands.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销》、《品牌管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">品牌定位；品牌定位钻石模型；品牌整合营销策略；品牌资产五星模型</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-01</td>
                            </tr>
